    <body>
      <head>Hilda [Hilde] Rothberger</head>

      <div>
        <p>Wife of <ref cRef="rothberger_alfred"
            >Alfred Rothberger</ref>, with whom she had two sons and a daughter.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <head>Correspondence with the Schenkers</head>
        
        <p>There is substantial correspondence from Hilda Rothberger to Heinrich and Jeanette
          Schenker dating between 1929 and 1938 as OJ 13/31 (30 items) and OC 38/489, 44/34-35,
          A/295. She is also frequently mentioned in Schenker's diaries.</p>
      </div>
    </body>
      
